    {
      "para_id": "Q001095.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(3) The personal god of En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu’s reed shrine of the high temple , is Šul-MUŠxPA ."
